{"tid":1456721,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"個人對機場諗法","createTime":"2019-08-12T10:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:57:25.000Z","uid":186743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bedb102614649472e47c10763d3888bbcc4dc756","tid":1456721,"uid":186743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:39:53.000Z","msg":"我覺得黑警未必會係機場清場，始終機場係一個對國際迴響大嘅地方，之後如果清場，機場點都會癱幾日，宜加反而我覺得警犬係到係想嚇走你地一但離開先開始打，5係機場開打，不過始終5係現場，真實情況靠前線手足自行判斷。香港人加油"},{"pid":"6ce143cd4bdffcc6cc8771f7579ff2a90fd24de3","tid":1456721,"uid":186743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:41:03.000Z","msg":"如果我係錯勿屌，只係一介市民嘅諗法"},{"pid":"4dae8ba2adb81b65509aa37436b5155d27f01a03","tid":1456721,"uid":186743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:47:39.000Z","msg":"同宜加睇落去警犬係機場附近道路設防，所以我真係覺得佢地係想嚇離機場內啲人，然後係外面發癲"},{"pid":"3885d55200581cc38b149aefb2c467cd67363edf","tid":1456721,"uid":186743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:53:15.000Z","msg":"自己推一推"},{"pid":"8a933dcfd50bfc6e0f288cab231724b14f2c89db","tid":1456721,"uid":186743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:53:44.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"0ec0bd1496ea60a27ab15447a89992cb59d245eb","tid":1456721,"uid":186743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:54:25.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"db728d29cc1bc58757d07abb8740b7e4bdbe535e","tid":1456721,"uid":186743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:56:21.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"55c188941f60adf78bb13bc44c19a7fd19d63c3f","tid":1456721,"uid":186743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:57:25.000Z","msg":"希望推到有人睇"}]}